    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_17_4142-4220",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "4142-4220",
      "markText": "孤独就是无求于人，我渴望得到孤独，天长日久，我总算获得了它。孤独是冰冷的，噢，是啊，它又是那样的恬静，那样的广阔无垠，像那又冷又静、群星回旋的宇宙空间一样。",
      "totalCount": 3726,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4142&rangeEnd=4220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4142&rangeEnd=4220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_18_3897-3961",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "3897-3961",
      "markText": "追求权力的人毁于权力，追求金钱的人毁于金钱，低声下气的人毁于卑躬屈膝，追求享乐的人毁于行乐。正是同样的道理，荒原狼毁于我行我素。",
      "totalCount": 2640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3897&rangeEnd=3961",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3897&rangeEnd=3961"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_22_595-694",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "595-694",
      "markText": "不管这是高度的智慧还是最简单的天真幼稚，谁能尽情享受瞬间的快乐，谁总是生活在现在，不瞻前顾后，谁懂得这样亲切谨慎地评价路边的每一朵小花，评价每个小小的、嬉戏的瞬间价值，那么生活就不能损害他一丝一毫。",
      "totalCount": 1830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=595&rangeEnd=694",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=595&rangeEnd=694"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_13_2615-2669",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2615-2669",
      "markText": "他认为，人们必须用具有永恒价值的信仰去代替时代的偶像，而这信仰就是对莫扎特和不朽者的崇敬，对人性的执着追求。",
      "totalCount": 1690,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2615&rangeEnd=2669",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2615&rangeEnd=2669"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_27_10726-10770",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "10726-10770",
      "markText": "我总有一天会更好地学会玩这人生游戏。我总有一天会学会笑。帕勃罗在等着我，莫扎特在等着我。",
      "totalCount": 1650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=10726&rangeEnd=10770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=10726&rangeEnd=10770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_14_5780-5954",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "5780-5954",
      "markText": "“爱人”与恨己都已同样深深地扎根于他的心中。他的一生告诉我们，不能自爱就不能爱人，憎恨自己也必憎恨他人，最后也会像可恶的自私一样，使人变得极度孤独和悲观绝望。",
      "totalCount": 1635,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=5780&rangeEnd=5954",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=5780&rangeEnd=5954"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_21_12455-12522",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "12455-12522",
      "markText": "人们会发现，这一切正像今天刚刚发展起的无线电一样，只能使人逃离自己和自己的目的，使人被消遣和瞎费劲儿的忙碌所织成的越来越密的网所包围。",
      "totalCount": 1520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=12455&rangeEnd=12522",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=12455&rangeEnd=12522"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_17_6285-6353",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "6285-6353",
      "markText": "我房间里，靠椅、炉子、墨水瓶、画盒、诺瓦利斯、陀思妥耶夫斯基正等着我归来，就像母亲或妻子、孩子、使女和狗、猫等着别的、正常的人回家一样。",
      "totalCount": 1395,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=6285&rangeEnd=6353",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=6285&rangeEnd=6353"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_14_13165-13238",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "13165-13238",
      "markText": "他知道自己孑然一身，不属于这个世界，但是他不会自杀，因为他残留的一点信仰告诉他，他必须把这种苦难，心中邪恶的苦难，忍受到生命终结，他只能受苦而死。",
      "totalCount": 1245,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=13165&rangeEnd=13238",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=13165&rangeEnd=13238"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_13_1417-1480",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1417-1480",
      "markText": "他既有人性，又有兽性，既有高尚光明的一面，又有庸俗阴暗的一面；他憎恨小市民，又习惯于小市民的生活；他憎恨秩序，又摆脱不了秩序。",
      "totalCount": 1140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1417&rangeEnd=1480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1417&rangeEnd=1480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_19_2768-2854",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2768-2854",
      "markText": "实际上，没有一个人是纯粹的单体，连最天真幼稚的人也不是，每个“我”都是一个非常复杂的世界，一个小小的星空，是由无数杂乱无章的形式、阶段和状况、遗传性和可能性组成的混沌王国。",
      "totalCount": 1080,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2768&rangeEnd=2854",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2768&rangeEnd=2854"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_16_3497-3561",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3497-3561",
      "markText": "不必为过去的事感到遗憾。遗憾的是现在和今天，是所有这些我失去的不可计数的日日夜夜，这些日子给我带来的既非厚礼也非震惊，而是痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 1024,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3497&rangeEnd=3561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3497&rangeEnd=3561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_17_3093-3167",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3093-3167",
      "markText": "有谁在他那生活的废墟上寻找支离破碎的人生意义，忍受似乎是荒唐的事情，过着似乎是疯子的生活，暗中却在最后的迷惑的混乱中希望能接近上帝，得到上帝的启示？",
      "totalCount": 920,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25291560&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3093&rangeEnd=3167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6c328207181eb28e6cdb43?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3093&rangeEnd=3167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25291560_14_8731-8802",
